  <para>If <parameter>node</parameter> has the <literal>linenumbering</literal> attribute set to <literal>"numbered"</literal>, then this
  template will create line numbers for each line, using the <function><link linkend="T__db_linenumbering">db.linenumbering</link></function>
  template.</para>
  </body>
